ning.</li>\r\n 	<li>Just pull out in front of TEC as he/she approaches unless youre indicated to do so. He/she may have traffic following close behind or some other situation youre not aware of. This could be potentially dangerous.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"102\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"102\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'RIDE ETIQUETTE', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '93-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-05-19 08:27:07', '2019-05-19 08:27:07', '', 93, 'http://localhost/underscore_2019/2019/05/19/93-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
