(193, 1, '2019-05-19 10:45:54', '2019-05-19 10:45:54', '<h1>CCC trg.UAE</h1>\r\nThis program is divided into mainly four sessions. They are as follow:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>General Issues</li>\r\n 	<li>Specific Issues</li>\r\n 	<li>Working in Harmony</li>\r\n 	<li>Relationship building workshop</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAbu Dhabi &amp; Dubai are fast growing centers of trade and finance in the Middle East. Primarily controlled free enterprise with many new Arab billionaires rapidly expanding their empires globally. Two cities with over 66% of the total population. Industrial, commercial &amp; financial clusters.\r\nThe cultures are based on three different basis like Eastern culture is based on Confucius, Western culture is based on Socrates, Arab culture is based on Islam &amp; tribal traditions\r\n\r\nSix cultural differences between Australia and Arab is:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Individualism  Collectivism</li>\r\n 	<li>Short Term  Short Term</li>\r\n 	<li>Low Power distance  High Power distance</li>\r\n 	<li>Direct Communication Time is their friend</li>\r\n 	<li>Low Uncertainty Avoidance  Hign Uncertainty Avoidance</li>\r\n 	<li>Quantity Quantity &amp; Quality of life</li>\r\n</ul>', 'CCC trg.UAE', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ccc-trg-uae', '', '', '2019-05-19 10:47:23', '2019-05-19 10:47:23', '', 0, 'http://localhost/underscore_2019/?p=193', 0, 'post', '', 0),
