(197, 1, '2019-05-19 10:56:55', '2019-05-19 10:56:55', '<h1>An SVC Approach 2</h1>\r\n<h2>SUSTAINABLE ENTERPRISE  RISK MANAGEMENT OVERVIEW</h2>\r\nThe effective use of resources and processes to allow an enterprise to capitalize on opportunities so as to provide sustainable returns for shareholders, and the greatest protection for all stakeholders  both now and in the future.\r\n\r\nThere are six strategies of sustainability and risk management.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Diversification Strategies (David)\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Concentric</li>\r\n 	<li>Conglomerate</li>\r\n 	<li>Horizontal</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Defensive Strategies\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Joint venture, buy out, strategic alliance, value chain alignment</li>\r\n 	<li>Retrenchment</li>\r\n 	<li>Divestiture</li>\r\n 	<li>Liquidation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Vertical Integration Strategies\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Forward</li>\r\n 	<li>Backward</li>\r\n 	<li>Horizontal</li>\r\n 	<li>Keiretsus, Chaebols</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Intensive Strategies (Ansoff)\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Market penetration</li>\r\n 	<li>Market development</li>\r\n 	<li>Product development</li>\r\n 	<li>Liquidation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Generic Strategies (Porter)\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Differentiation</li>\r\n 	<li>Cost Leadership</li>\r\n 	<li>Focus</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Avoidance Strategies\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Management by Extrapolation</li>\r\n 	<li>Management by Crisis</li>\r\n 	<li>Management by Subjectives</li>\r\n 	<li>Management by Hope</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'An SVC Approach 2', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'an-svc-approach-2', '', '', '2019-05-19 10:56:55', '2019-05-19 10:56:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/underscore_2019/?p=197', 0, 'post', '', 0),
