(225, 1, '2019-05-21 11:52:35', '2019-05-21 11:52:35', '[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" css=\".vc_custom_1558244668617{margin-top: -20px !important;}\"][vc_column][rev_slider_vc alias=\"HOME\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1558246979945{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"About Ian Kirkwood\" font_container=\"tag:h1|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal\"][vc_separator align=\"align_left\"][vc_column_text]Academic, Lecturer, Director  specializing in Strategic Business Sustainability\r\n\r\nAs a practical academic, he runs the MBA program with James Cook Uni in Brisbane. Always on the lookout for projects or internships for our best and brightest students. There is zero cost and confidentiality of results is always maintained. He comes as part of the package to steer the internship or develop a specifically targeted project. The goal of Mr. Ian Kirkwood is to help businesses make more money and become more sustainable.\r\n\r\nThe students at James Cook University, specializing in strategic sustainability, Marketing, Hospitality, IT, and Accounting. He has been involved in lecturing and consulting since 2008 with decades of prior experience across a broad range of industries, local and global. As a result of his background, he focuses on producing students who have a real focus on producing results  particularly for SME companies.\r\n\r\nHis two great passions are motorcycling, and helping businesses become realistically sustainability.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1558247707195{padding-top: 50px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"68\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" style=\"vc_box_shadow_3d