ss-cultural intelligence[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Certificates\" font_container=\"tag:h1|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal\"][vc_separator align=\"align_left\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]Certificates\r\n Justice of the Peace (Qualified)\r\n\r\nLicense JP (Qual)\r\n December 2016  Present\r\n\r\n MAICD\r\n\r\nAust. Inst. of Company Directors\r\n PhD in cross cultural business\r\n\r\n TAE40110 Training &amp; Assessment\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css=\".vc_custom_1558251114659{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;background-color: #008080 !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"BE THE FIRST TO GET THE UPDATES\" font_container=\"tag:h1|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][contact-form-7 id=\"87\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1558246979945{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Motorcycling\" font_container=\"tag:h1|text_align:center\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal\"][vc_separator el_width=\"50\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Dr. Ian Kirkwood has an interest in biking with the groups. He often used to go for a ride in the group to different locatio